{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781459239581,"sessionID":"ses_138c2bb01ffeUjkBZZt6lKZbis","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_0d3ae2e37e49493d82a7dcb0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Dashboard\n\nAuto-generated. Overwritten each iteration.\n\n## Status\n- **Provisional Verdict**: PENDING\n- **hasAdvisories**: false\n- **Release Readiness**: in-progress\n- **Iteration**: 0 of 10\n- **Mode**: review\n\n## Findings Summary\n| Severity | Active | New This Iteration |\n|----------|--------|-------------------|\n| P0 | 0 | 0 |\n| P1 | 0 | 0 |\n| P2 | 0 | 0 |\n\n## Progress Table\n| Run | Status | Focus | Dimensions | Ratio | Duration |\n|-----|--------|-------|------------|-------|----------|\n\n## Coverage\n- **Dimensions completed**: 0/4\n- **Files reviewed**: 0\n- **Traceability protocols**: core=pending, overlay=pending\n\n## Trend\n- Rolling average: N/A\n- Composite stop score: 0.00\n- Trajectory: N/A\n\n## Active Risks\n- None detected\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781459239577,"end":1781459239580}},"id":"prt_ec73ec297001oqVGl4hzLllzi8","sessionID":"ses_138c2bb01ffeUjkBZZt6lKZbis","messageID":"msg_ec73eac38001HYw0foMVMbL7NE"}}
