 forward) |\n <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n \n ---\n \n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-strategy.md","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-strategy.md\n@@ -46,8 +46,9 @@\n | Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n |-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n | D1 Correctness | CONDITIONAL | 1 | 2 P1 (yolo running-state gap, install.sh error handling), 3 P2 |\n | D2 Security | PASS | 2 | 0 P0/P1, 2 P2 (tool name mismatch in snippet, doctor running-state check) |\n+| D3 Traceability | PASS | 3 | 0 P0/P1/P2 new; all 4 protocols pass (F005 from iter 1 carried forward) |\n <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n \n ---\n \n","additions":1,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/151-mcp-figma-with-direct-cli-support/review/session-audit/lineages/mimo-v25-pro/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781459473632,"end":1781459473633}},"id":"prt_ec74254dd001hxLX1Gr3ICviD5","sessionID":"ses_138c2bb01ffeUjkBZZt6lKZbis","messageID":"msg_ec74244b4001uzfcFC5B7Ynomy"}}
